name: Raunchy Runtz
description: Raunchy Runtz is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Cream D and Runtz. This strain is 40% sativa and 60% indica. Raunchy Runtz is 20% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Bred by Exotic Genetics, the average price of Raunchy Runtz typically ranges from $10-$15 per gram.
